Package online.labrary.javaByContract

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ContractEnforcer
    The class that enforces contracts expressed in @Invariant, @Precondition and @Postcondition annotations.
  • Error Summary 
    Error Description
    ContractViolationException
    A runtime error that signals that an object's contract was violated.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Invariant
    Express a class or interface invariant.
    Invariants
    A collection annotation, so that a class or interface can have multiple Invariants.
    Postcondition
    Express a method postcondition.
    Postconditions
    A collection annotation, so that a method can have multiple Postconditions.
    Precondition
    Express a method precondition.
    Preconditions
    A collection annotation, so that a class or interface can have multiple Preconditions.
